laxies.\nAs an alternative to dark matter, introducing an effective weak field potential\nfor MOG opens a new window to the astrophysical applications of the theory.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 27 Jun 2013 00:00:21 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 20 Aug 2013 12:03:25 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 17 Sep 2013 22:07:30 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Thu, 19 Sep 2013 10:18:08 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-16"}
